1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:01,810
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,810 --> 00:00:03,380
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,080
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:09,580
You must've hidden Baek Jin Ju
somewhere else,

5
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,620
but I'll catch her in the end.

6
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,550
I've already sent my men
to the press conference...

7
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:17,890
and the review committee hearing.

8
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,690
Catch her if you can.

9
00:00:21,730 --> 00:00:23,460
That's assuming Jin Ju is even
at any of those places.

10
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,160
What?

11
00:00:25,730 --> 00:00:27,830
Don't tell me this was all a trick.

12
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:29,200
That's right.

13
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,140
This time, you're the one
who played right into our hands.

14
00:00:34,910 --> 00:00:38,480
Now what happened seven years ago
will be revealed to the world,

15
00:00:39,180 --> 00:00:43,180
and the review committee
will decide to reinvestigate.

16
00:00:44,050 --> 00:00:45,320
Unlike what happened 30 years ago,

17
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,920
the statute of limitations
hasn't expired for this,

18
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:49,390
so you won't be able
to escape legal punishment.

19
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:56,590
Where's Baek Jin Ju?

20
00:00:57,860 --> 00:01:00,300
Where is she, and what's she up to?

21
00:01:04,070 --> 00:01:07,810
(Incident Behind)

22
00:01:07,870 --> 00:01:11,740
To hide the fact
that he murdered Kim Myung Hui,

23
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:14,350
Chairman Park killed my father
to eliminate the evidence,

24
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:16,920
staging it as an accident.

25
00:01:17,580 --> 00:01:21,550
I got back on my feet
to clear my father's name,

26
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:24,560
and I've requested
a police reinvestigation.

27
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:27,060
Right now,

28
00:01:27,790 --> 00:01:30,090
the reinvestigation review committee
should be in session.

29
00:01:30,330 --> 00:01:32,460
(Temi Bio to Be Reinvestigated?)

30
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:35,800
So that the reinvestigation
is approved,

31
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,500
I'm calling on everyone for help.

32
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:41,940
(Temi Bio to Be Reinvestigated?)

33
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:43,210
Please.

34
00:01:43,210 --> 00:01:46,280
(Temi Bio to Be Reinvestigated?)

35
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,780
(Reinvestigate Former Adele Group
Chairman Park Tae Ho)

36
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:50,650
Arrest Park Tae Ho!

37
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:52,420
- Arrest him!
- Arrest him!

38
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,950
A reinvestigation is
the only answer.

39
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,590
Approve the reinvestigation.

40
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,560
- Approve it!
- Approve it!

41
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,660
Okay, everyone,
make sure the signs are clear.

42
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,930
Please use "ParkTaeHo"
and "Reinvestigation..."

43
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,460
as the hashtags.

44
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:11,300
(Reinvestigate Former Adele Group
Chairman Park Tae Ho)

45
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,680
Park Tae Ho,

46
00:02:22,650 --> 00:02:25,780
you tried to use my guilt to drive
a wedge between Jin Ju and me.

47
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:30,050
Your plan has failed completely.

48
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,820
I'll protect Jin Ju,

49
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:35,760
and together, we'll reveal the truth
from seven years ago.

50
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:38,660
That's right.

51
00:02:39,330 --> 00:02:42,170
In the end, we'll win.

52
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,700
Park Tae Ho!

53
00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:46,100
You may be alone,

54
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,540
but we have each other.

55
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:58,550
The review committee just approved
the reinvestigation.

56
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,520
What?

57
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:05,160
Sir, it's true.

58
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:09,060
No, how dare they...

59
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:14,530
You said I led Dr. Baek
to his death.

60
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:18,600
Because I was trying to uncover
the truth from 30 years ago.

61
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:21,010
Those words will come back...

62
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:22,910
to strike you down,

63
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,510
Park Tae Ho.

64
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:28,510
Revealing the truth
about Dr. Baek's accident...

65
00:03:29,350 --> 00:03:32,820
will bring your vile motive
for murder to light.

66
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:37,990
It'll prove you killed my sister
30 years ago.

67
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,920
At least that way,

68
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,890
you'll finally pay
for my sister's death.

69
00:03:43,490 --> 00:03:45,160
No...

70
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:49,200
Who dares make me pay for anything?

71
00:03:50,230 --> 00:03:51,340
This isn't over yet.

72
00:03:52,370 --> 00:03:53,610
Just you wait.

73
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,110
Come on!

74
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:07,920
Has a reinvestigation
really been approved?

75
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,720
Yes.

76
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:13,060
This time, not even Park Tae Ho
can wriggle out of it.

77
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:15,390
The same goes
for the others involved...

78
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:17,000
in the incident
from seven years ago.

79
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:28,010
Immediately after the accident,
Temi Bio Korea's CEO, Choi Sam Sik,

80
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,980
accused CEO Baek of embezzlement...

81
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,580
and framed his death as a suicide.

82
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:34,680
What the...

83
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:36,950
He's talking about you, right?

84
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:38,520
- At the time,
- Does the whole world...

85
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,950
the police concluded
it was a simple accident...

86
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,790
know what I did?

87
00:04:43,290 --> 00:04:48,030
A key witness has come forward
to turn this case on its head.

88
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:50,300
Hello?

89
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,000
Yes?

90
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,700
Yes, this is Choi Sam Sik.

91
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,940
A reinvestigation?

92
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:05,340
Oh my. Honey, what...

93
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,710
The police...

94
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,980
are reopening the case
from seven years ago.

95
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,690
They want me to come in
for questioning.

96
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:16,220
Oh no, what do we do?

97
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:17,820
Oh dear.

98
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:19,920
I'm finished.

99
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:23,760
The police already suspect me.

100
00:05:24,730 --> 00:05:26,800
Look, there's nothing
to be scared of.

101
00:05:28,670 --> 00:05:31,940
Park Tae Ho's the one
who forced you into this, right?

102
00:05:32,170 --> 00:05:35,440
Just tell the police
how it all went down.

103
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:39,540
It'll be okay.

104
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:42,680
There's nothing to worry about.

105
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:44,650
Oh dear.

106
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,990
The reinvestigation team has been
formed and has started its work.

107
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:52,890
An emergency arrest is imminent.

108
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:56,060
I told the legal team to handle it.

109
00:05:56,890 --> 00:05:59,700
Sir, the Adele Group's legal team...

110
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,530
won't be able to handle this.

111
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:05,570
What? How so?

112
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:06,970
Well,

113
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:09,410
the shareholder backlash is
too severe.

114
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:18,920
Tell that murderer,
Chairman Park Tae, Ho to step down.

115
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:20,920
Do you know how much
the stock price has dropped?

116
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,350
- Cut ties with that murderer.
- Park Tae Ho, get down here!

117
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,260
Don't stop me!

118
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,890
Fix this, Park Tae Ho.

119
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:29,290
Park Tae Ho!

120
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:31,560
- What?
- Come out, now.

121
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:34,300
As the son
of former Chairman Park Tae Ho,

122
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:38,670
here's my official statement
regarding the Temi Bio uproar.

123
00:06:39,570 --> 00:06:42,310
Please distribute it
to the shareholders and the press.

124
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:45,440
An official statement?

125
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,950
I'm exposing my father's crimes...

126
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:50,250
and reporting him.

127
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:53,250
No!

128
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:59,260
Park Min Jun, are you insane?

129
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,690
Regardless of everything,
the chairman is your father.

130
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,690
Unlike the past incident,
the statute of limitations...

131
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,060
won't bury this one.

132
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:08,130
He could be arrested immediately.

133
00:07:08,330 --> 00:07:11,540
Yes, fortunately,
the crimes from seven years ago...

134
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,010
are still prosecutable.

135
00:07:15,470 --> 00:07:19,110
You'll also be held
legally responsible.

136
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:26,950
Understood.

137
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:30,690
The chairman...

138
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:33,860
won't go down that easily.

139
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:41,900
We'll see.

140
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:44,800
I wonder if he can really
get away with it.

141
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:53,240
If the legal team can't do it,
hire some lawyers...

142
00:07:53,810 --> 00:07:54,880
and form a response team!

143
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,710
Yes, sir.

144
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:03,090
Defending a murderer?

145
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,560
The legal fees will be astronomical.

146
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:08,590
What are you blabbering about?

147
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:10,090
I'm just saying...

148
00:08:10,090 --> 00:08:14,300
that kind of money
could buy a cleaner solution.

149
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:17,400
A lady I know used
the money for lawyers...

150
00:08:17,470 --> 00:08:19,000
to hire a stand-in instead.

151
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,470
A stand-in?

152
00:08:22,170 --> 00:08:23,440
Maybe you should...

153
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:27,510
try to find someone
to take the fall for you.

154
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,320
Sir.

155
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:38,620
I heard they decided
to reinvestigate.

156
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:41,190
So, what's going to happen to me?

157
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:43,330
I'm not going
to be investigated too, am I?

158
00:08:50,570 --> 00:08:51,570
That's right.

159
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:56,270
It's all your fault
that things have gone this wrong.

160
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:59,940
Because you failed
to kill Baek Jin Ju!

161
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,380
You're going to have
to take responsibility...

162
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,590
for everything Baek Jin Ju has done.

163
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:19,800
Have you been waiting long?

164
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:23,200
No, I was at the office
and just got here.

165
00:09:23,770 --> 00:09:25,000
You heard the news, right?

166
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:28,540
- The case will be reopened.
- Yes, it's such a relief.

167
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:31,010
Now that the investigation
is reopened...

168
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,280
and the shareholders
are putting pressure,

169
00:09:33,410 --> 00:09:35,310
he won't be able
to harm you anymore.

170
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,380
Hello.

171
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,020
Director, you're here too.

172
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:42,090
Oh, right.

173
00:09:42,450 --> 00:09:43,450
Hello.

174
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:45,620
Thank you for all your help,

175
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,830
from producing the documentary
to appearing on the show.

176
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:52,260
Not at all. The project is getting
so much buzz...

177
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:54,130
that I'm actually the one
who benefited.

178
00:09:54,470 --> 00:09:56,730
By the way,
did Director Park Hyun Jun...

179
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,840
not come with you?

180
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,070
Right. I'm afraid not.

181
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:03,310
It's just that
we had to rush the broadcast,

182
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:05,410
so it's a shame we couldn't
include an interview...

183
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,640
with Director Park Hyun Jun.

184
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:09,250
Would it be possible
to interview him at a later time?

185
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:12,120
If you need one,
I can do it instead.

186
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:15,720
I'm Chairman Park Tae Ho's son too.

187
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:17,720
Yes, that would work.

188
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:20,960
I'll take you up on that later.
I'll be in touch.

189
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:22,330
Thank you.

190
00:10:27,730 --> 00:10:30,530
Hyun Jun was supposed
to do an interview?

191
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:32,700
Yes.

192
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:38,610
By the time the documentary airs,
I'll be the chairman of Adele.

193
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,840
At that point,

194
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:42,880
I'll reveal the truth...

195
00:10:44,050 --> 00:10:46,280
and make you the chairman of Adele.

196
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:48,790
That's my plan,

197
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:51,990
my apology to you,

198
00:10:55,930 --> 00:10:56,960
and proof of my love.

199
00:10:58,830 --> 00:10:59,900
But I...

200
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:04,270
have nothing to give you.

201
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,370
You've already given me everything.

202
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,440
A place by your side.

203
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:22,820
If they reopen the investigation,
what do you think will happen?

204
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:25,620
Even someone like Park Tae Ho
will end up in prison, won't he?

205
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,590
Then that's good for us.

206
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:32,860
Even if it's revealed
that you're not Park Tae Ho's son,

207
00:11:32,930 --> 00:11:33,930
what does it matter?

208
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:39,170
As long as we're in control
of Adele Group, it's game over.

209
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:42,470
So should we just do nothing
and wait?

210
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:46,110
We should at least pretend
to be concerned.

211
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:56,250
Director Seo.
I wasn't expecting a call.

212
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:59,090
Is this about Park Tae Ho
being investigated by the police?

213
00:12:00,190 --> 00:12:02,490
This won't have any effect
on Hyun Jun becoming chairman...

214
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:05,630
What?

215
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,770
What kind of nonsense is that?

216
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,980
- You're here.
- Hey.

217
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,750
You did great.

218
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:25,250
It's all thanks to your help.

219
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:28,250
Now we just need the reinvestigation
to go smoothly.

220
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:31,260
Right. Just a little further,

221
00:12:31,260 --> 00:12:32,660
and we'll finally put
an end to this.

222
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:37,190
Until Park Tae Ho is in prison,
let's all keep up the fight.

223
00:12:41,170 --> 00:12:42,730
Is anyone here?

224
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:50,640
Mrs. Han, how did you...

225
00:12:50,810 --> 00:12:54,080
I'm here because
something urgent came up.

226
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:57,380
How did you know our address?

227
00:12:57,520 --> 00:13:01,450
We, at Ihwachae,
know more than you realize.

228
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,660
Here, have some tea.

229
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:16,330
The major shareholder, Moon Tae Jin,

230
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,870
gave his opinion
on the chairman election?

231
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,000
Yes.

232
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:22,770
After watching the broadcast
and the documentary today,

233
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:24,910
it seems he formed his opinion.

234
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:29,110
"I cannot accept
a candidate recommended..."

235
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:30,680
"by a murderer like Park Tae Ho."

236
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:33,420
"If Park Tae Ho is arrested
by the police,"

237
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:36,950
"Park Hyun Jun must also
be disqualified as a candidate."

238
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:43,930
Hold on.

239
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:48,400
It's certain that Moon Tae Jin
is supporting Dan Hui.

240
00:13:48,770 --> 00:13:49,770
Yes.

241
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:52,870
Now, once Chairman Park is arrested,

242
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,440
you must prepare to become
the new chairman.

243
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:00,880
And this.

244
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:08,550
It's an apartment unit I own.

245
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:11,990
I hear that Chairman Park
and Oh Jung Ran...

246
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,490
keep showing up unannounced.

247
00:14:15,890 --> 00:14:18,600
Once the chairman election
is in full swing,

248
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:22,000
they might become
more of a nuisance.

249
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:26,970
You should consider moving
somewhere quieter.

250
00:14:27,570 --> 00:14:29,570
I've always wondered...

251
00:14:29,970 --> 00:14:33,680
if there was reason you're going
to such lengths to help me?

252
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:38,520
Didn't I tell you
from the very beginning?

253
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:43,190
I wanted to support you
on your journey.

254
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:47,120
Now, I also want to see...

255
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:50,490
Park Tae Ho punished
for his evil deeds.

256
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:04,880
Moon Tae Jin.

257
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:08,210
Why is some guy
who's never shown his face interfering?

258
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,780
He's the majority shareholder,

259
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,350
so of course he's interested
in the chairman selection.

260
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,850
Acting like this...

261
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:19,890
just proves the majority shareholder
is behind Kim Dan Hui.

262
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:22,830
The board members...

263
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:25,400
will find it hard to ignore
the majority shareholder's opinion.

264
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:30,470
Once Park Tae Ho is arrested,
Hyun Jun's candidacy is over.

265
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:32,940
That's why we have to stop it.

266
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:36,310
If I want to remain
a candidate for chairman,

267
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,340
we have to prevent his arrest.

268
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:40,980
Hyun Jun...

269
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:43,480
Hey, Park Hyun Jun.

270
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:54,660
The reinvestigation seems
to be moving rather quickly.

271
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:58,000
I think the police are going
to make an emergency arrest.

272
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:00,730
Because of the public outcry,

273
00:16:01,970 --> 00:16:03,630
you're just going to put on a show?

274
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:07,000
They could show up
as early as tomorrow.

275
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:10,610
Anyway, if you get arrested,

276
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:12,010
I'm just going to walk away.

277
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:15,180
So just pay me
the compensation you promised.

278
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:17,350
Why, you....

279
00:16:21,590 --> 00:16:23,190
- Father.
- Please don't tell me...

280
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:24,790
you're getting arrested.

281
00:16:27,260 --> 00:16:30,060
You show up now
and pretend to be worried?

282
00:16:30,430 --> 00:16:31,760
Is it because
the majority shareholder...

283
00:16:32,030 --> 00:16:35,500
threatened to disqualify
Park Hyun Jun as a candidate?

284
00:16:35,930 --> 00:16:37,900
Is this really the time for that?

285
00:16:37,970 --> 00:16:40,540
We need to work together
to stop the arrest.

286
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,240
That's what's important.

287
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:45,710
Yes. I'll do whatever it takes
to help you, Father.

288
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:49,950
Just buy me some time.
Keep the police from showing up.

289
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:51,120
Stop them at all costs.

290
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:54,180
If you know anyone useful
in the police force,

291
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:55,350
make an introduction.

292
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:59,760
Even so, you can't stop
an emergency arrest.

293
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:03,490
Can't we at least buy a few days,
like my father said?

294
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:06,000
Well, in that case,

295
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:08,600
I suppose I could arrange a meeting.

296
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:12,900
I'll go meet them myself...

297
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,070
in my father's place.

298
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:24,520
(Adele)

299
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:33,360
This is the money
the chairman prepared.

300
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:37,430
Okay.

301
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:40,030
I'll leave right away.

302
00:17:42,230 --> 00:17:43,870
No, wait.

303
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:47,500
Hyun Jun, this isn't right.

304
00:17:47,670 --> 00:17:50,770
You don't need to be running errands
delivering money yourself.

305
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,910
Money?

306
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:02,750
Hyun Jun, what are you trying to do?

307
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:07,590
Whatever I'm doing, stay out of it.

308
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,790
But... Wait.

309
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:14,300
To remain a candidate for chairman,

310
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,330
are you trying to stop
Father's arrest?

311
00:18:16,330 --> 00:18:19,470
Are you going to keep getting
in Jin Ju's way on behalf of Father?

312
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,240
Jin Ju.

313
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:27,380
Weren't you the one
who saved her life?

314
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,980
You were worried enough
about Jin Ju to save her,

315
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:32,720
so why are you doing this?

316
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,630
It seems Jin Ju
didn't tell you everything.

317
00:18:43,290 --> 00:18:45,930
I saved her,
but that's where it ends.

318
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:49,030
From now on,
I'm not doing this for her,

319
00:18:50,430 --> 00:18:52,170
but for myself.

320
00:18:56,410 --> 00:18:58,980
Hyun Jun!

321
00:19:12,390 --> 00:19:16,130
All you're doing is buying him time,

322
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:19,260
but that is a huge bag of money.

323
00:19:19,330 --> 00:19:21,900
Stop drooling over it,

324
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,200
and let's go inside.

325
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:31,640
Arrogant punk.

326
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:41,720
I can't believe he made Hyun Jun
do this kind of dirty work.

327
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:44,090
What on earth...

328
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:46,920
is Chairman Park thinking?

329
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:59,100
What are you doing here?

330
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:02,740
I told you that you'd have
to take responsibility for what you did.

331
00:20:03,870 --> 00:20:06,180
What exactly do you expect me to do?

332
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:15,150
You used me to kill them both!

333
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,960
You made me get blood on my hands.

334
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:26,200
Because of you, I...

335
00:20:26,630 --> 00:20:28,100
Unbelievable!

336
00:20:29,970 --> 00:20:32,140
You're saying
some very dangerous things.

337
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,710
Do you have any evidence
that I ordered you?

338
00:20:36,870 --> 00:20:38,040
That's...

339
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:43,650
Framing an innocent person
without evidence is a crime!

340
00:20:45,980 --> 00:20:47,520
And on top of that,

341
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:50,050
you've admitted
to being an accomplice...

342
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,460
to murder.

343
00:20:57,690 --> 00:20:58,760
That means...

344
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:03,470
there's a lot I can do
with this evidence.

345
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:10,140
What are you going to do
with that recording?

346
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:12,310
I have proof here...

347
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:14,780
that you're an accomplice
to Baek Jun Gi's murder.

348
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:20,050
All I have to do is testify
that Choi Sam Sik was involved too.

349
00:21:21,050 --> 00:21:24,760
If I get arrested now,

350
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:28,490
you and Choi Sam Sik
will be finished too.

351
00:21:30,230 --> 00:21:32,830
Baek Jin Ju will get what she wants.

352
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:37,630
- Oh, no.
- Goodness. Oh, honey.

353
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,640
Who says it's over?

354
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:42,040
I won't let you
ruin my life like this.

355
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:45,580
Then we need to sort this out...

356
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:48,150
in a way that minimizes the damage.

357
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:52,420
Then, what exactly
are you proposing?

358
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:57,490
Choi Sam Sik,
say that you did everything,

359
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:58,760
and turn yourself in.

360
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:02,260
- Sir!
- What?

361
00:22:02,430 --> 00:22:04,260
Are you telling me...

362
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:07,700
to take the fall for everything?

363
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:10,230
If you make this sacrifice,

364
00:22:10,730 --> 00:22:12,840
I'll make sure
you're well compensated.

365
00:22:20,610 --> 00:22:23,780
We'll clear the foreclosure
on this house,

366
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:30,220
and you'll never have to worry
about money again.

367
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:34,360
I ought to sew your mouth shut.

368
00:22:34,690 --> 00:22:37,490
How dare you spout such nonsense?

369
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,860
You can offer me the world,

370
00:22:38,930 --> 00:22:41,300
but my husband isn't going
to become a murderer,

371
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,470
so get out while I ask nicely.

372
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:47,940
Turn yourself in
to the police tomorrow morning.

373
00:22:48,710 --> 00:22:50,070
If you don't,

374
00:22:51,010 --> 00:22:53,340
Choi Sam Sik, I'll frame both you...

375
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,080
and your daughter...

376
00:22:56,250 --> 00:22:58,380
for murder.

377
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:02,650
Goodness. Honestly.

378
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:06,820
Those scum!

379
00:23:07,460 --> 00:23:09,760
Oh, honey. Oh, gosh.

380
00:23:10,930 --> 00:23:12,300
Honey, wait.

381
00:23:14,430 --> 00:23:17,530
Why Choi Sam Sik and not Choi Yu Na?

382
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:23,970
A child is the perfect hostage
to hold against a parent. Right?

383
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:27,040
Why do you think I involved
Choi Yu Na in the first place?

384
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:31,520
It was so I could use her like this.
You just don't get it.

385
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:36,650
He's so infuriating
at times like this.

386
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,960
Wait.

387
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:44,430
What? Have you decided already?

388
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:46,760
Is the compensation guaranteed?

389
00:23:47,230 --> 00:23:49,100
If my dad takes the fall
for everything,

390
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:52,070
are you really going to protect us?

391
00:23:55,570 --> 00:23:57,440
Just stop Park Tae Ho
from getting arrested.

392
00:23:58,110 --> 00:24:00,240
If that buys Hyun Jun enough time
to become chairman,

393
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:03,510
I'll make sure you're taken care of,
not Park Tae Ho.

394
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,650
You can keep your position
as team leader...

395
00:24:05,650 --> 00:24:07,620
and get enough money
to last a lifetime.

396
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:09,150
That's not good enough.

397
00:24:09,950 --> 00:24:13,020
I need a more concrete,
guaranteed reward.

398
00:24:13,190 --> 00:24:15,960
What compensation
could be more definite than money?

399
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:20,200
I'm going to have to
marry Park Hyun Jun.

400
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:23,370
What? Marry him?

401
00:24:24,530 --> 00:24:27,440
You're making my father a murderer.
It's the least I deserve.

402
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:30,710
I can't live as a murderer's daughter,
with everyone pointing fingers at me.

403
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:33,780
I need to become a part
of the Adele Group.

404
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:39,220
Fine.
Marriage isn't a big deal anyway.

405
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:41,020
He almost married Baek Jin Ju,
after all.

406
00:24:42,950 --> 00:24:45,690
Just make sure
your father goes to prison.

407
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:48,330
That's the only way
Hyun Jun can become chairman.

408
00:24:48,860 --> 00:24:52,530
You'd better not go back
on your word.

409
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:55,870
I'll expose Hyun Jun's secret
to the chairman...

410
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:58,270
and have him kicked out
of the Adele family.

411
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:03,710
Get your father to agree first
before you threaten me.

412
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:18,460
What did you just say?

413
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,720
Yu Na?

414
00:25:22,860 --> 00:25:26,100
Dad, take the fall for everything
and turn yourself in.

415
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,870
Have you lost your mind?

416
00:25:28,870 --> 00:25:30,030
What choice do we have?

417
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:32,540
Should Dad and I both go to prison?

418
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:34,700
You don't care if my life is ruined?

419
00:25:36,040 --> 00:25:40,010
Parents are meant to protect
their children's future.

420
00:25:40,610 --> 00:25:42,910
How dare you
say something like that?

421
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:44,920
Do you have a better idea?

422
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:52,390
What's the alternative?
Should we all just go down together?

423
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:53,960
Besides,

424
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:56,960
Dad doesn't do anything
at home anyway.

425
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:59,760
What's the difference between
him being at home or in prison?

426
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:01,870
In that case,
he might as well be in...

427
00:26:02,930 --> 00:26:03,970
Honey!

428
00:26:07,570 --> 00:26:10,840
I see I raised you wrong.

429
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:15,580
I did a truly terrible job
raising you.

430
00:26:16,210 --> 00:26:19,420
Even if the whole world
pointed its finger at you,

431
00:26:21,020 --> 00:26:24,390
as your mother,
because you're my child,

432
00:26:25,620 --> 00:26:28,860
I told myself I should just
embrace you tighter.

433
00:26:28,990 --> 00:26:30,960
That's how I raised you!

434
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:32,500
How...

435
00:26:33,260 --> 00:26:36,700
How could you stab me in the heart?

436
00:26:37,230 --> 00:26:42,110
How could you throw your own parents
into a pit of fire...

437
00:26:42,170 --> 00:26:44,070
just to save your own skin?

438
00:26:45,010 --> 00:26:47,310
Because I refuse
to live a pathetic life!

439
00:26:48,610 --> 00:26:49,610
What was that?

440
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:52,320
Why do you think
I tried to kill Baek Jin Ju?

441
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:56,650
Dad was always sucking up
to CEO Baek.

442
00:26:56,790 --> 00:26:59,120
And you were always fawning
over Baek Jin Ju.

443
00:27:00,690 --> 00:27:04,430
It was because I didn't want to live
a pathetic life like you two.

444
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:05,730
Back then,

445
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:08,200
I was afraid we'd be ruined
like we are now,

446
00:27:08,260 --> 00:27:09,800
so I was the one
who saved our family.

447
00:27:10,300 --> 00:27:11,600
So then...

448
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:17,410
Now it's your turn to save
our family and my future, Dad.

449
00:27:17,670 --> 00:27:20,540
Choi Yu Na, that's enough.

450
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:22,210
- You rotten brat!
- Don't!

451
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:24,510
Honey, please.

452
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:26,580
You decide, Dad.

453
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:30,220
Should we all rot in prison
and lose everything,

454
00:27:31,550 --> 00:27:34,890
or are you going to sacrifice
your insignificant life to save us?

455
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:39,360
The decision is yours.

456
00:27:43,170 --> 00:27:45,670
My gosh. Choi Yu Na!

457
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:48,170
That girl!

458
00:27:48,370 --> 00:27:51,570
Honey, oh no. Stay with me!

459
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:55,780
What do we do?

460
00:27:56,450 --> 00:27:59,420
What am I going to do
with that girl?

461
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:02,290
Oh, my. Goodness.

462
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:10,260
Are you really going to move
into this house?

463
00:28:11,460 --> 00:28:12,860
Just as Mrs. Han said,

464
00:28:13,060 --> 00:28:16,070
Park Tae Ho has been dropping by
Yoon Jung's house as he pleases.

465
00:28:17,100 --> 00:28:18,870
Considering what's left to do,

466
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:22,540
I think it's a good idea to move
to a place he doesn't know about.

467
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:25,780
If you need a place to stay,
we can prepare one for you.

468
00:28:26,410 --> 00:28:27,410
That's all right.

469
00:28:27,910 --> 00:28:30,750
I think I'll go along with
what Mrs. Han has kindly arranged.

470
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:33,820
It seems she has a plan of her own.

471
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:35,850
Don't worry about us.

472
00:28:36,220 --> 00:28:38,720
Jin Ju, you just focus
on the reinvestigation.

473
00:28:40,090 --> 00:28:42,530
You never know what else
Park Tae Ho might do,

474
00:28:42,830 --> 00:28:44,560
so be extremely careful.

475
00:28:45,130 --> 00:28:46,800
Okay, don't worry.

476
00:28:48,100 --> 00:28:50,430
They reopened the investigation,

477
00:28:50,870 --> 00:28:52,340
so why hasn't Park Tae Ho
been arrested?

478
00:28:52,340 --> 00:28:53,370
I'm not sure.

479
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:55,740
The police aren't making a move.

480
00:28:57,010 --> 00:28:59,840
I think my father
is lobbying the police.

481
00:29:01,010 --> 00:29:02,010
Hyun Jun...

482
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:05,420
I saw him leave
with a bag full of money.

483
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:08,590
- What?
- Hyun Jun did what?

484
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:12,560
I'll have to put some pressure
on the police.

485
00:29:17,090 --> 00:29:20,830
I'll also find out
how they're planning to interfere.

486
00:29:21,460 --> 00:29:22,470
Okay.

487
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:43,450
Sir, I just heard
from Detective Yun.

488
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:46,690
The police are planning to make
an emergency arrest today.

489
00:29:50,190 --> 00:29:51,230
What?

490
00:29:51,690 --> 00:29:54,930
We paid them all that money,
and all it bought us was one day?

491
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,030
It seems that Baek Jin Ju
and JKL Partners...

492
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:00,000
put pressure on them.

493
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:02,110
Darn it!

494
00:30:02,840 --> 00:30:04,970
You! What about Choi Sam Sik?

495
00:30:05,810 --> 00:30:07,410
I'll check on it right now.

496
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:10,680
I'll go with her.

497
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:13,050
Can you two do nothing right?

498
00:30:13,850 --> 00:30:16,520
Stop the police from setting foot
in my house!

499
00:30:24,890 --> 00:30:26,330
Actually, no.

500
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:30,300
Just in case, prepare for the worst.

501
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:31,900
Yes, sir.

502
00:30:42,150 --> 00:30:44,250
Tell me what's going on.

503
00:30:44,250 --> 00:30:46,550
What are they doing on their end...

504
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:48,420
to prevent my father's arrest?

505
00:30:49,990 --> 00:30:52,790
I don't know anything.

506
00:30:52,890 --> 00:30:55,120
Hyun Jun is delivering
the bribes himself.

507
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:57,260
Are you just going
to let this happen?

508
00:30:57,690 --> 00:31:00,700
Don't come to me with this.
Instead...

509
00:31:02,300 --> 00:31:05,670
You might want to check on
what Ms. Choi's father is planning.

510
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:09,170
You mean CEO Choi Sam Sik?

511
00:31:13,810 --> 00:31:14,810
Are you saying...

512
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:30,790
So this is where the information
is leaking from.

513
00:31:31,690 --> 00:31:32,800
Hyun Jun...

514
00:31:33,730 --> 00:31:37,270
Look into CEO Choi Sam Sik
right now.

515
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:42,810
(Police)

516
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:51,550
Right.

517
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:54,380
I'm the head of this family,

518
00:31:55,390 --> 00:31:56,950
a husband, and a father.

519
00:31:58,820 --> 00:31:59,820
I have to do this.

520
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,060
Mr. Choi!

521
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,060
What do you think you're doing?

522
00:32:08,730 --> 00:32:11,370
Are you going to be
Park Tae Ho's lapdog again?

523
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:45,200
(Pearl in Red)

524
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:48,370
What was Park Tae Ho thinking,
pulling a stunt like this?

525
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:51,310
Cover-ups and fabrication
are his expertise, aren't they?

526
00:32:51,570 --> 00:32:52,940
He must've had a way
to handle it discreetly.

527
00:32:53,010 --> 00:32:54,010
Oh, dear.

528
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:56,610
How could you tell me
to take the fall for everything?

529
00:32:56,950 --> 00:32:59,350
- How could you...
- The choice is yours!

530
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:02,220
You can either fight me
and hit rock bottom,

531
00:33:02,390 --> 00:33:05,620
or end this now and save yourself.

532
00:33:05,890 --> 00:33:09,730
Then how should I live?
Should I live like you, as your son?

533
00:33:09,790 --> 00:33:11,430
- Park Hyun Jun.
- This!

534
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:15,230
This is the path I've chosen.
Who are you to decide it's wrong?

535
00:33:16,330 --> 00:33:18,300
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
